<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>BARBERSHOP JAMES</title>
  <meta name="description" content="APLICACION PLAYSTORE"/>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --gold: #e4a64f;
      --gold2: #f5c97a;
      --dark: #090909;
      --card: #141416;
      --border: rgba(228,166,79,.2);
      --text: #f0ede8;
      --muted: #7a7570;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--dark);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 600px; height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(228,166,79,.07) 0%, transparent 65%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .g-bar {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg,
        #4285f4 0%, #4285f4 25%,
        #ea4335 25%, #ea4335 50%,
        #fbbc05 50%, #fbbc05 75%,
        #34a853 75%);
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 52px 44px;
      max-width: 480px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      animation: rise .7s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1) both;
      box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    }

    @keyframes rise {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .logo {
      width: 88px; height: 88px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(228,166,79,.25);
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .sub {
      font-size: .82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: .04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .explain {
      background: rgba(228,166,79,.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(228,166,79,.18);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .explain p {
      font-size: .84rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .explain p strong {
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .btn {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 12px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 18px 24px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #111;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: .95rem;
      transition: transform .18s, box-shadow .18s;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(0,0,0,.5); }
    .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }
    .btn img { width: 26px; height: 26px; object-fit: contain; }
    .btn-text { text-align: left; }
    .btn-text small { display: block; font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 400; color: #666; }

    .tags {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .tag {
      font-size: .73rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 4px 12px;
    }
    .tag span { color: #34a853; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="g-bar"></div>

  <div class="card">
    <img class="logo"
      src="https://i.ibb.co/JFrnTqWc/c4497cf0-2f10-43bf-b5ac-6c232c4d0e18.jpg"
      alt="James Barbershop"/>

    <h1>Barbershop James</h1>
    <div class="sub">Aplicación en Google Play Store</div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="explain">
      <p>
        Estamos lanzando nuestra app de reservas y necesitamos personas que
        la <strong>prueben gratis</strong> antes del lanzamiento oficial.<br/><br/>
        Si te unes, solo tienes que <strong>usarla durante 15 días</strong>
        — sin costo, sin tarjeta, sin complicaciones.
        Tu ayuda hace que la app llegue a más personas. 🙌
      </p>
    </div>

    <a class="btn"
      href="https://play.google.com/apps/testing/jamesbarber.app.reservas?hl=es"
      target="_blank">
      <img src="https://www.freepnglogos.com/uploads/play-store-logo-png/google-play-store-logo-png-transparent-png-logos-10.png" alt="Play Store"/>
      <div class="btn-text">
        <small>Descargar gratis en</small>
        <span>Google Play — Unirme a la prueba</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <div class="tags">
      <div class="tag"><span>✓</span> Gratis</div>
      <div class="tag"><span>✓</span> Sin tarjeta</div>
      <div class="tag"><span>✓</span> 15 días</div>
      <div class="tag"><span>✓</span> Sin compromiso</div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
